    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在比特币活动上发表讲话，表达对加密货币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/trump-to-address-bitcoin-event-in-show-of-crypto-support</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据活动组织者称，唐纳德·特朗普将于本月在比特币会议上发表演讲，此次演讲将凸显他对加密货币行业的日益支持。彭博社的 Sonali Basak 与 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 一起参加了“彭博科技”节目。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-11/trump-to-address-bitcoin-event-in-show-of-crypto-support</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 20:19:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级抵押贷款机构加大对经纪人赢得再融资的奖励力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/top-mortgage-lender-sweetens-rewards-for-brokers-to-win-refis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[顶级抵押贷款机构 United Wholesale Mortgage 正在加大对其经纪人网络提供某些类型住房贷款的激励力度，此举可能会加速再融资，从而对抵押贷款支持证券的购买者产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/top-mortgage-lender-sweetens-rewards-for-brokers-to-win-refis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2024 20:13:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
